  "title": "Technological Approaches to Human Performance Enhancement",
  "abstract": "This report provides an examination of three possible modalities for generating human performance enhancement (HPE): genetic modifications, artificial intelligence, and Internet of Bodies approaches in which devices implanted in or worn by a human are connected to a network. This report provides an overview of the potential for each modality, the state of the enabling technologies, and the associated challenges (both technical and ethical).",
